data.description: Discover this gem in Eagle River, where every inch is smartly utilized to create a cozy yet spacious home. Picture yourself in the inviting kitchen, or unwinding in the living room, with the convenience of the main bedroom, laundry, and a neat half bath all on the first floor. Head upstairs to find a comfy family room, another large bedroom, and a full bath, perfect for family or guests.This place redefines 'condo' living, feeling more like a duplex with its private yard and homey vibe. Plus, enjoy mountain views that add a touch of tranquility to your day.  The homeowner's association is all about making life easier. Dues take care of the not-so-fun stuff like trash, sewer, and water services. You won't have to worry about lawn care (outside the fence), snow shoveling, or road upkeep. Plus, they've got the exterior maintenance covered - from painting to roof upkeep, and even the driveway.  It's not just a home; it's a lifestyle upgrade with a view!
